480
00:44:49,354 --> 00:44:50,854
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Stop!</font></b>

481
00:44:53,566 --> 00:44:54,858
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No!</font></b>

482
00:44:57,945 --> 00:45:01,323
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, gosh! Oh, gods! Oh, no!</font></b>

483
00:45:01,741 --> 00:45:04,868
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">All right, OK, you've gotta
