00:45:49,664 --> 00:45:51,289
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yeah!</font></b>

486
00:45:53,126 --> 00:45:54,209
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Come on.</font></b>

487
00:46:03,261 --> 00:46:05,178
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No, thanks. I'm good.</font></b>

488
00:46:42,216 --> 00:46:45,343
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Not so fireproof on
the inside, are you?</font></b>

489
00:46:45,511 --> 00:46:46,636
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Here you go.</font></b>

490
00:47:03,196 --> 00:47:07,324
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Everything we know about
you guys is wrong.</font></b>

491
00:47:17,543 --> 00:47:20,504
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Dad! You're back!
Gobber's not here so...</font></b>

492
00:47:20,671 --> 00:47:21,671
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I know.</font></b>

493
00:47:24,258 --> 00:47:27,093
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- I came looking for you.
- You did?</font></b>

494
00:47:27,261 --> 00:47:28,762
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You've been keeping secrets.</font></b>

495
00:47:29,096 --> 00:47:30,472
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I have?</font></b>

496
00:47:30,640 --> 00:47:33,266
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Just how long did you
think you could hide it?</font></b>

497
00:47:33,434 --> 00:47:36,102
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I don't know what you're...</font></b>

498
00:47:36,270 --> 00:47:40,690
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Nothing happens on this island
without me hearing about it.</font></b>

499
00:47:41,484 --> 00:47:42,776
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">So...</font></b>

500
00:47:43,486 --> 00:47:47,447
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">let's talk...
...about that dragon.</font></b>

501
00:47:47,615 --> 00:47:51,785
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, gods. Dad, I'm so sorry.
I was going to tell you.</font></b>

502
00:47:52,119 --> 00:47:54,371
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I just didn't know how to...</font></b>

503
00:47:59,168 --> 00:48:01,294
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You're not upset?</font></b>

504
00:48:01,462 --> 00:48:04,089
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What?! I was hoping for this!</font></b>

505
00:48:04,966 --> 00:48:07,634
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- You were?
- And believe me, it only gets better!</font></b>

506
00:48:07,802 --> 00:48:10,554
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Wait till you spill a
Nadder's guts the first time!</font></b>

507
00:48:10,721 --> 00:48:13,431
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And mount your first
Gronckle head on a spear!</font></b>

508
00:48:13,599 --> 00:48:17,394
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What a feeling! You really
had me going there, son!</font></b>

509
00:48:17,562 --> 00:48:21,731
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">All those years of the worst
Viking Berk has ever seen.</font></b>

510
00:48:21,899 --> 00:48:25,193
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Odin, it was rough. I
almost gave up on you.</font></b>

511
00:48:25,361 --> 00:48:27,612
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And all the while you
were holding out on me!</font></b>

512
00:48:27,780 --> 00:48:29,656
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, Thor Almighty!</font></b>

513
00:48:31,450 --> 00:48:33,827
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">With you doing so
well in the ring...</font></b>

514
00:48:35,162 --> 00:48:37,831
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">we finally have
something to talk about.</font></b>

515
00:48:51,554 --> 00:48:55,181
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Here, I brought you something,</font></b>

516
00:48:55,433 --> 00:48:58,143
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">to keep you safe in the ring.</font></b>

517
00:48:58,311 --> 00:49:00,395
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Wow. Thanks.</font></b>

518
00:49:00,563 --> 00:49:02,991
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Your mother would have
wanted you to have it.</font></b>

519
00:49:03,004 --> 00:49:05,442
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's half of her breastplate.</font></b>

520
00:49:07,028 --> 00:49:10,864
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Matching set. It keeps
her close, you know.</font></b>

521
00:49:11,574 --> 00:49:16,578
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Wear it proudly. You deserve it.
You've held up your end of the deal.</font></b>

522
00:49:22,209 --> 00:49:26,546
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- I should really get to bed.
- Yes, good. OK, good talk.</font></b>

523
00:49:26,714 --> 00:49:29,132
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- I'll see you back at the house. Great.
- We should do this again.</font></b>

524
00:49:29,300 --> 00:49:30,508
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Thanks for stopping by...</font></b>

525
00:49:30,676 --> 00:49:33,720
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- ...and for the breast hat.
- I hope you like the hat.</font></b>

526
00:49:35,723 --> 00:49:37,599
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well... Yep. Good night.</font></b>

527
00:49:52,573 --> 00:49:55,575
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Stay out of my way! I'm
winning this thing.</font></b>

528
00:49:55,743 --> 00:49:58,453
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Please, by all means.</font></b>

529
00:50:10,508 --> 00:50:12,592
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">This time, this time for sure!</font></b>

530
00:50:21,435 --> 00:50:24,187
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No! No, son of a half-troll,</font></b>

531
00:50:24,355 --> 00:50:27,357
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- rat-eating, munge-bucket!
- Wait, wait.</font></b>

532
00:50:27,525 --> 00:50:29,359
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- So, later.
- Not so fast.</font></b>

533
00:50:29,527 --> 00:50:31,486
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- I'm kind of late for...
- What?!</font></b>

534
00:50:31,654 --> 00:50:34,197
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Late for what, exactly?</font></b>

535
00:50:34,365 --> 00:50:37,200
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Quiet down! The
elder has decided.</font></b>

536
00:50:48,629 --> 00:50:52,882
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You've done it, Hiccup! You
get to kill the dragon!</font></b>

537
00:50:56,178 --> 00:50:57,345
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That's my boy!</font></b>

538
00:50:57,513 --> 00:51:01,224
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yeah. Yes. I can't wait.
I am so...</font></b>

539
00:51:01,392 --> 00:51:03,309
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">leaving! We're leaving.</font></b>

540
00:51:03,477 --> 00:51:07,939
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Let's pack up. Looks like you and
me are taking a little vacation.</font></b>

541
00:51:08,399 --> 00:51:09,649
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Forever.</font></b>

542
00:51:12,403 --> 00:51:13,945
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, man.</font></b>

543
00:51:15,906 --> 00:51:18,992
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What the?! What are
you doing here?</font></b>

544
00:51:19,827 --> 00:51:22,245
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I want to know what's going on.</font></b>

545
00:51:22,413 --> 00:51:26,499
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No one just gets as good as you do.
Especially you.</font></b>

546
00:51:26,667 --> 00:51:29,502
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Start talking! Are you
training with someone?</font></b>

547
00:51:29,670 --> 00:51:30,712
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Training?</font></b>

548
00:51:30,880 --> 00:51:32,505
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It better not involve this.</font></b>

549
00:51:32,673 --> 00:51:36,301
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I know this looks really
bad, but you see...</font></b>

550
00:51:38,679 --> 00:51:40,680
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You're right. You're right.
You're right.</font></b>

551
00:51:40,848 --> 00:51:45,977
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm through with the lies. I've
been making outfits. So you got me.</font></b>

552
00:51:46,312 --> 00:51:50,273
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's time everyone knew. Drag
me back, go ahead. Here we go.</font></b>

553
00:51:50,858 --> 00:51:52,400
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Why would you do that?!</font></b>

554
00:51:52,568 --> 00:51:56,988
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That's for the lies. And
that's for everything else.</font></b>

555
00:51:57,782 --> 00:51:58,782
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, man.</font></b>

556
00:52:00,242 --> 00:52:01,242
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Get down!</font></b>

557
00:52:03,204 --> 00:52:04,579
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Run, run!</font></b>

558
00:52:07,208 --> 00:52:09,000
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's OK! It's OK.</font></b>

559
00:52:09,335 --> 00:52:10,710
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">She's a friend.</font></b>

560
00:52:12,880 --> 00:52:14,214
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You just scared him.</font></b>

561
00:52:14,381 --> 00:52:15,882
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I scared him?!</font></b>

562
00:52:16,884 --> 00:52:18,510
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Who is "him"?</font></b>

563
00:52:19,595 --> 00:52:23,598
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Astrid, Toothless.
Toothless, Astrid.</font></b>

564
00:52:29,730 --> 00:52:30,897
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">We're dead.</font></b>

565
00:52:31,899 --> 00:52:34,025
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Where do you think you're going?</font></b>

566
00:52:40,157 --> 00:52:43,034
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, great Odin's ghost!
This is it!</font></b>

567
00:52:53,921 --> 00:52:56,256
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hiccup, get me down from here!</font></b>

568
00:52:56,423 --> 00:52:58,591
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You have to give me a
chance to explain.</font></b>

569
00:52:58,759 --> 00:53:01,427
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I am not listening to
anything you have to say!</font></b>

570
00:53:01,595 --> 00:53:05,056
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Then I won't speak.
Just let me show you.</font></b>

571
00:53:06,600 --> 00:53:07,976
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Please, Astrid.</font></b>

572
00:53:23,951 --> 00:53:25,034
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Now get me down.</font></b>

573
00:53:25,202 --> 00:53:27,954
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Toothless, down. Gently.</font></b>

574
00:53:29,748 --> 00:53:32,458
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">See? Nothing to be afraid of.</font></b>

575
00:53:35,880 --> 00:53:37,338
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Toothless!</font></b>

576
00:53:38,340 --> 00:53:41,342
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What is wrong with you?!
Bad dragon!</font></b>

577
00:53:42,469 --> 00:53:45,346
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He's not usually like this.
Oh, no.</font></b>

578
00:53:50,895 --> 00:53:54,022
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Toothless, what are you doing?
We need her to like us!</font></b>

579
00:53:57,026 --> 00:53:59,027
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And now the spinning.</font></b>

580
00:53:59,904 --> 00:54:03,072
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Thank you for nothing,
you useless reptile.</font></b>

581
00:54:03,824 --> 00:54:06,826
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">OK, I am sorry! I'm sorry.</font></b>

582
00:54:07,119 --> 00:54:08,828
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Just get me off of this thing.</font></b>

583
00:55:55,519 --> 00:55:59,230
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">All right, I admit it.
This is pretty cool.</font></b>

584
00:55:59,565 --> 00:56:02,108
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's amazing.</font></b>

585
00:56:02,443 --> 00:56:03,985
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He's amazing.</font></b>

586
00:56:06,655 --> 00:56:08,781
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">So what now?</font></b>

587
00:56:08,949 --> 00:56:11,784
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hiccup, your final
exam is tomorrow.</font></b>

588
00:56:12,077 --> 00:56:14,078
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You know you'll have to kill...</font></b>

589
00:56:14,663 --> 00:56:15,788
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">kill a dragon.</font></b>

590
00:56:15,956 --> 00:56:17,665
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Don't remind me.</font></b>

591
00:56:18,792 --> 00:56:20,209
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Toothless, what's happening?</font></b>

592
00:56:22,671 --> 00:56:24,088
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What is it?</font></b>

593
00:56:26,884 --> 00:56:27,967
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Get down!</font></b>

594
00:56:45,235 --> 00:56:46,986
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- What's going on?
- I don't know.</font></b>

595
00:56:47,154 --> 00:56:50,156
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Toothless, you gotta get
us out of here, bud.</font></b>

596
00:56:52,701 --> 00:56:55,119
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It looks like they're
hauling in their kill.</font></b>

597
00:56:56,080 --> 00:56:57,830
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What does that make us?</font></b>

598
00:57:40,749 --> 00:57:43,251
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What my Dad wouldn't
give to find this.</font></b>

599
00:58:00,185 --> 00:58:03,646
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's satisfying to know that all of
our food has been dumped down a hole.</font></b>

600
00:58:04,314 --> 00:58:06,649
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">They're not eating any of it.</font></b>

601
00:58:22,124 --> 00:58:23,749
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What is that?</font></b>

602
00:58:30,883 --> 00:58:33,885
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">All right, bud, we got to
get out of here... now!</font></b>

603
00:58:43,270 --> 00:58:47,064
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It totally makes sense.
It's like a giant beehive.</font></b>

604
00:58:47,232 --> 00:58:49,233
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">They're the workers and
that's their queen.</font></b>

605
00:58:49,401 --> 00:58:51,944
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It controls them.
Let's find your Dad.</font></b>

606
00:58:52,112 --> 00:58:53,362
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No! No.</font></b>

607
00:58:53,697 --> 00:58:57,783
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No, not yet. They'll
kill Toothless.</font></b>

608
00:58:57,951 --> 00:59:00,661
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">We have to think this
through carefully.</font></b>

609
00:59:00,829 --> 00:59:03,748
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hiccup, we just discovered
the dragons' nest,</font></b>

610
00:59:03,916 --> 00:59:06,626
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">the thing we've been after since
Vikings first sailed here,</font></b>

611
00:59:06,793 --> 00:59:09,086
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">and you want to
keep it a secret?</font></b>

612
00:59:09,254 --> 00:59:12,173
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">To protect your pet dragon?
Are you serious?</font></b>

613
00:59:14,301 --> 00:59:15,509
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yes.</font></b>

614
00:59:22,976 --> 00:59:25,478
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">OK. Then what do we do?</font></b>

615
00:59:25,646 --> 00:59:29,398
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Just give me until tomorrow.
I'll figure something out.</font></b>

616
00:59:30,150 --> 00:59:31,317
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">OK.</font></b>

617
00:59:32,861 --> 00:59:34,153
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That's for kidnapping me.</font></b>

618
00:59:41,161 --> 00:59:43,871
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That's for everything else.</font></b>

619
00:59:53,048 --> 00:59:55,049
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What are you looking at?</font></b>

620
00:59:55,801 --> 00:59:59,929
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hiccup! Hiccup! Hiccup! Hiccup!</font></b>

621
01:00:02,766 --> 01:00:06,143
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I can show my face
in public again!</font></b>

622
01:00:08,480 --> 01:00:11,565
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">If someone had told me
that in a few short weeks.</font></b>

623
01:00:11,733 --> 01:00:16,320
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hiccup would go from,
well, being Hiccup</font></b>

624
01:00:16,488 --> 01:00:20,992
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">to placing first in dragon training,
well, I would have tied him to a mast</font></b>

625
01:00:21,159 --> 01:00:23,744
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">and shipped him off for
fear he'd gone mad!</font></b>

626
01:00:24,413 --> 01:00:25,746
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And you know it!</font></b>

627
01:00:28,208 --> 01:00:32,712
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">But here we are. And no
one is more surprised</font></b>

628
01:00:32,879 --> 01:00:35,881
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">or more proud than I am.</font></b>

629
01:00:36,383 --> 01:00:39,802
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Today, my boy becomes a Viking.</font></b>

630
01:00:39,970 --> 01:00:43,180
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Today, he becomes one of us!</font></b>

631
01:00:47,185 --> 01:00:49,061
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Be careful with that dragon.</font></b>

632
01:00:49,229 --> 01:00:52,648
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- It's not the dragon I'm worried about.
- What are you going to do?</font></b>

633
01:00:52,816 --> 01:00:55,901
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Put an end to this.
I have to try.</font></b>

634
01:00:56,611 --> 01:01:00,031
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Astrid, if something goes wrong,</font></b>

635
01:01:00,198 --> 01:01:02,241
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">just make sure they
don't find Toothless.</font></b>

636
01:01:02,909 --> 01:01:06,454
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I will. Just promise
me it won't go wrong.</font></b>

637
01:01:07,205 --> 01:01:10,458
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's time, Hiccup.
Knock 'em dead.</font></b>

638
01:01:16,006 --> 01:01:18,466
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yeah! Show 'em how it's done.</font></b>

639
01:01:18,633 --> 01:01:21,886
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hiccup! Hiccup! Hiccup! Hiccup!</font></b>

640
01:01:34,399 --> 01:01:35,941
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I would have gone
for the hammer.</font></b>

641
01:01:40,072 --> 01:01:41,280
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm ready.</font></b>

642
01:02:05,305 --> 01:02:07,932
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Go on, Hiccup. Give it to him!</font></b>

643
01:02:12,354 --> 01:02:13,687
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What is he doing?</font></b>

644
01:02:16,483 --> 01:02:19,110
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hey, it's OK. It's OK.</font></b>

645
01:02:26,993 --> 01:02:28,160
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm not one of them.</font></b>

646
01:02:33,333 --> 01:02:34,542
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What's he thinking?</font></b>

647
01:02:35,127 --> 01:02:36,585
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Stop the fight.
- No!</font></b>

648
01:02:37,045 --> 01:02:39,463
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I need you all to see this.</font></b>

649
01:02:40,382 --> 01:02:42,508
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">They're not what
we think they are.</font></b>

650
01:02:43,260 --> 01:02:44,677
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">We don't have to kill them.</font></b>

651
01:02:46,179 --> 01:02:48,389
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I said, stop the fight!</font></b>

652
01:02:55,939 --> 01:02:57,148
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Out of my way!</font></b>

653
01:02:57,399 --> 01:02:57,899
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hiccup!</font></b>

654
01:03:27,262 --> 01:03:28,554
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">This way!</font></b>

655
01:03:48,909 --> 01:03:50,159
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Night Fury!</font></b>

656
01:04:08,762 --> 01:04:10,554
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Toothless, go. Get out of here.</font></b>

657
01:04:12,766 --> 01:04:13,933
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Go, go!</font></b>

658
01:04:14,100 --> 01:04:15,100
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Stoick, no!</font></b>

659
01:04:15,268 --> 01:04:16,644
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Dad, he won't hurt you!</font></b>

660
01:04:17,646 --> 01:04:20,689
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No, don't! You're
only making it worse!</font></b>

661
01:04:21,816 --> 01:04:22,816
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Toothless, stop!</font></b>

662
01:04:24,611 --> 01:04:26,445
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No! No!</font></b>

663
01:04:30,075 --> 01:04:31,075
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Get him!</font></b>

664
01:04:34,663 --> 01:04:36,664
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No, no! Please just
don't hurt him!</font></b>

665
01:04:37,374 --> 01:04:38,791
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Please don't hurt him.</font></b>

666
01:04:45,757 --> 01:04:47,258
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Put it with the others.</font></b>

667
01:04:50,053 --> 01:04:52,513
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I should have known. I
should have seen the signs.</font></b>

668
01:04:52,681 --> 01:04:54,515
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Dad?
- We had a deal!</font></b>

669
01:04:54,683 --> 01:04:58,727
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I know we did. That was before...
It's all so messed up.</font></b>

670
01:04:58,895 --> 01:05:02,314
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">So everything in the ring, a trick?
A lie?</font></b>

671
01:05:02,482 --> 01:05:06,610
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I screwed up. I should have
told you before now. I just...</font></b>

672
01:05:06,778 --> 01:05:10,322
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Take this out on me, be mad at me, but
please, just don't hurt Toothless.</font></b>

673
01:05:10,490 --> 01:05:13,659
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The dragon? That's what
you're worried about?</font></b>

674
01:05:13,827 --> 01:05:15,536
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Not the people you
almost killed?</font></b>

675
01:05:15,704 --> 01:05:18,122
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He was protecting me!
He's not dangerous.</font></b>

676
01:05:18,290 --> 01:05:20,291
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">They've killed hundreds of us!</font></b>

677
01:05:20,458 --> 01:05:22,167
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And we've killed
thousands of them!</font></b>

678
01:05:22,335 --> 01:05:27,590
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">They defend themselves, that's all!
They raid us because they have to.</font></b>

679
01:05:27,757 --> 01:05:31,594
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">If they don't bring enough food
back, they'll be eaten themselves.</font></b>

680
01:05:31,761 --> 01:05:36,056
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">There's something else on their island.
It's a dragon like...</font></b>

681
01:05:36,224 --> 01:05:38,976
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Their island? So you've
been to the nest?</font></b>

682
01:05:39,144 --> 01:05:40,936
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Did I say nest?
- How did you find it?</font></b>

683
01:05:41,104 --> 01:05:43,647
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What? No, I didn't.
Toothless did.</font></b>

684
01:05:43,815 --> 01:05:46,525
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Only a dragon can
find the island.</font></b>

685
01:05:47,861 --> 01:05:50,988
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No, no, no. No, Dad. No, please,
it's not what you think.</font></b>

686
01:05:51,156 --> 01:05:54,199
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You don't know what you're up against.
It's like nothing you've ever seen.</font></b>

687
01:05:54,367 --> 01:05:58,287
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Dad, please. I promise you,
you can't win this one!</font></b>

688
01:05:58,455 --> 01:06:00,497
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No, Dad. No.</font></b>

689
01:06:00,665 --> 01:06:03,626
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">For once in your life, would
you please just listen to me?!</font></b>

690
01:06:07,380 --> 01:06:11,175
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You've thrown your lot in with them.
You're not a Viking.</font></b>

691
01:06:13,428 --> 01:06:15,304
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You're not my son.</font></b>

692
01:06:18,516 --> 01:06:19,767
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Ready the ships!</font></b>

693
01:06:31,780 --> 01:06:32,988
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">This way.</font></b>

694
01:07:15,323 --> 01:07:16,865
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Set sail!</font></b>

695
01:07:17,242 --> 01:07:19,618
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">We head for Helheim's Gate.</font></b>

696
01:07:28,128 --> 01:07:30,462
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Lead us home, devil.</font></b>

697
01:07:51,359 --> 01:07:52,860
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's a mess.</font></b>

698
01:07:54,195 --> 01:07:57,448
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You must feel horrible.
You've lost everything:</font></b>

699
01:07:57,615 --> 01:08:00,492
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Your father, your tribe,
your best friend.</font></b>

700
01:08:00,660 --> 01:08:02,828
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Thank you for summing that up.</font></b>

701
01:08:04,664 --> 01:08:08,167
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Why couldn't I have killed that
dragon when I found him in the woods?</font></b>

702
01:08:08,334 --> 01:08:12,629
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Would have been better for everyone.
- Yep. The rest of us would've done it.</font></b>

703
01:08:13,506 --> 01:08:15,340
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">So why didn't you?</font></b>

704
01:08:18,011 --> 01:08:20,804
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Why didn't you?
- I don't know.</font></b>

705
01:08:21,765 --> 01:08:23,682
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- I couldn't.
- That's not an answer.</font></b>

706
01:08:23,850 --> 01:08:26,143
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Why is this so important
to you all of a sudden?</font></b>

707
01:08:26,311 --> 01:08:29,521
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Because I want to remember
what you say right now.</font></b>

708
01:08:29,689 --> 01:08:32,200
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">For the love of... I was a coward.
I was weak.</font></b>

709
01:08:32,213 --> 01:08:34,735
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I wouldn't kill a dragon.</font></b>

710
01:08:34,903 --> 01:08:36,153
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You said "wouldn't".</font></b>

711
01:08:36,321 --> 01:08:38,489
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Whatever! I wouldn't!</font></b>

712
01:08:38,656 --> 01:08:42,534
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Three hundred years and I'm the first
Viking who wouldn't kill a dragon.</font></b>

713
01:08:47,040 --> 01:08:48,957
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">First one to ride one, though.</font></b>

714
01:08:51,419 --> 01:08:52,419
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">So?</font></b>

715
01:08:55,381 --> 01:08:58,759
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I wouldn't kill him because he
looked as frightened as I was.</font></b>

716
01:08:59,844 --> 01:09:03,430
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I looked at him
and I saw myself.</font></b>

717
01:09:05,266 --> 01:09:09,937
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I bet he's really frightened now.
What are you going to do about it?</font></b>

718
01:09:11,397 --> 01:09:15,901
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Probably something stupid.
- Good, but you've already done that.</font></b>

719
01:09:17,529 --> 01:09:19,530
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Then something crazy.</font></b>

720
01:09:20,406 --> 01:09:22,533
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That's more like it.</font></b>

721
01:09:31,000 --> 01:09:34,253
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Sound your positions.
Stay within earshot.</font></b>

722
01:09:34,420 --> 01:09:36,922
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Here!
- One length to your stern.</font></b>

723
01:09:37,340 --> 01:09:42,302
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Listen, Stoick, I was overhearing some
of the men and, well, some of them</font></b>

724
01:09:42,470 --> 01:09:46,098
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">are wondering what it is we're up to here.
Not me, of course.</font></b>

725
01:09:46,266 --> 01:09:48,767
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I know you're always the man
with the plan. But some,</font></b>

726
01:09:48,935 --> 01:09:52,437
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">not me, are wondering if there
is in fact a plan at all</font></b>

727
01:09:52,605 --> 01:09:56,233
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- and what it might be.
- Find the nest and take it.</font></b>

728
01:09:56,401 --> 01:09:58,527
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Of course. Send them running.</font></b>

729
01:09:58,695 --> 01:10:01,446
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The old Viking fallback.
Nice and simple.</font></b>

730
01:10:10,373 --> 01:10:12,040
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Step aside.</font></b>

731
01:10:25,388 --> 01:10:26,513
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Bear to port.</font></b>

732
01:10:31,477 --> 01:10:35,814
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">If you're planning on getting eaten,
I'd definitely go with the Gronckle.</font></b>

733
01:10:36,941 --> 01:10:40,986
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You were wise to seek help from
the world's most deadly weapon.</font></b>

734
01:10:41,154 --> 01:10:42,154
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's me.</font></b>

735
01:10:42,322 --> 01:10:44,698
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- I love this plan.
- I didn't...</font></b>

736
01:10:44,866 --> 01:10:47,743
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You're crazy. I like that.</font></b>

737
01:10:48,202 --> 01:10:50,579
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">So, what is the plan?</font></b>

738
01:11:00,757 --> 01:11:02,507
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That's not really encouraging.</font></b>

739
01:11:04,886 --> 01:11:06,970
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I was wondering where that went.</font></b>

740
01:11:18,942 --> 01:11:22,194
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Stay low and ready your weapons.</font></b>

741
01:11:37,877 --> 01:11:39,169
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">We're here.</font></b>

742
01:12:12,120 --> 01:12:14,621
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Wait! What are you?
- Relax.</font></b>

743
01:12:14,789 --> 01:12:16,999
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's OK. It's OK.</font></b>

744
01:12:28,678 --> 01:12:29,678
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Where are you going?</font></b>

745
01:12:29,846 --> 01:12:32,472
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You'll need something
to help you hold on.</font></b>

746
01:12:41,566 --> 01:12:45,736
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">When we crack this Mountain open,
all hell is going to break loose.</font></b>

747
01:12:45,903 --> 01:12:48,864
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">In my undies. Good thing
I brought extras.</font></b>

748
01:12:49,032 --> 01:12:52,284
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No matter how this
ends, it ends today.</font></b>

749
01:13:47,256 --> 01:13:49,007
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Is that it?</font></b>

750
01:13:53,679 --> 01:13:55,013
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">We've done it!</font></b>

751
01:14:03,898 --> 01:14:08,068
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">This isn't over! Form your ranks!
Hold together!</font></b>

752
01:14:21,207 --> 01:14:22,874
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Get clear!</font></b>

753
01:14:32,385 --> 01:14:34,928
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Beard of Thor! What is that?!</font></b>

754
01:14:39,142 --> 01:14:41,017
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Odin help us.</font></b>

755
01:14:45,815 --> 01:14:46,898
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Catapults!</font></b>

756
01:14:56,576 --> 01:14:58,952
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Get to the ships!
- No! No!</font></b>

757
01:15:11,841 --> 01:15:13,758
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Smart, that one.
- I was a fool.</font></b>

758
01:15:13,926 --> 01:15:16,094
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Lead the men to the far
side of the island!</font></b>

759
01:15:16,262 --> 01:15:17,429
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Gobber, go with the men!</font></b>

760
01:15:17,597 --> 01:15:20,557
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I think I'll stay, in case your
thinking of doing something crazy.</font></b>

761
01:15:20,725 --> 01:15:23,852
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I can buy them a few minutes if I
give that thing someone to hunt!</font></b>

762
01:15:24,020 --> 01:15:25,562
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Then I can double that time.</font></b>

763
01:15:28,274 --> 01:15:31,610
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Here!
- Oh, no! Here!</font></b>

764
01:15:41,746 --> 01:15:44,915
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Come on! Fight me!</font></b>

765
01:15:45,082 --> 01:15:46,958
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No, me!</font></b>

766
01:15:53,549 --> 01:15:55,800
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Ruff, Tuff! Watch your backs!</font></b>

767
01:15:55,968 --> 01:15:58,136
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Move, Fishlegs!</font></b>

768
01:15:58,304 --> 01:16:02,140
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Look at us! We're on a dragon.
We're on dragons! All of us!</font></b>

769
01:16:03,809 --> 01:16:06,102
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Up! Let's move it!</font></b>

770
01:16:06,604 --> 01:16:11,024
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Every bit the boar-headed
stubborn Viking you ever were!</font></b>

771
01:16:12,818 --> 01:16:14,444
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Fishlegs, break it down!
- OK.</font></b>

772
01:16:14,612 --> 01:16:17,405
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Heavily armored skull and tail
made for bashing and crushing!</font></b>

773
01:16:17,573 --> 01:16:19,563
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Steer clear of both. Small
eyes, large nostrils!</font></b>

774
01:16:19,576 --> 01:16:21,576
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Relies on hearing and smell!</font></b>

775
01:16:21,744 --> 01:16:25,121
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">OK, Lout, Legs! Hang in its blind
spot, make noise, keep it confused!</font></b>

776
01:16:25,289 --> 01:16:29,000
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Ruff, Tuff, find out if it has
a shot limit! Make it mad!</font></b>

777
01:16:29,168 --> 01:16:30,543
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That's my specialty!</font></b>

778
01:16:30,711 --> 01:16:34,005
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Since when?! Everyone knows
I'm more irritating! See.</font></b>

779
01:16:34,173 --> 01:16:37,425
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Just do what I told you! I'll
be back as soon as I can!</font></b>

780
01:16:37,843 --> 01:16:40,345
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Don't worry! We got it covered!
- Yeah!</font></b>

781
01:16:49,355 --> 01:16:50,397
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Troll!
- Butt elf!</font></b>

782
01:16:50,564 --> 01:16:52,107
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Bride of Grendel!</font></b>

783
01:16:57,905 --> 01:17:00,365
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">This thing doesn't
have a blind spot!</font></b>

784
01:17:03,160 --> 01:17:04,160
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">There!</font></b>

785
01:17:12,628 --> 01:17:13,795
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Go help the others!</font></b>

786
01:17:15,673 --> 01:17:17,048
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">OK, hold on. Hold on.</font></b>

787
01:17:21,012 --> 01:17:23,471
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- It's working!
- Yeah, it's working!</font></b>

788
01:17:33,107 --> 01:17:36,484
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I've lost power on the Gronckle!
Snotlout, do something!</font></b>

789
01:17:39,905 --> 01:17:41,448
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm OK!</font></b>

790
01:17:41,907 --> 01:17:43,074
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Less OK!</font></b>

791
01:17:45,745 --> 01:17:49,456
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I can't miss! What's wrong, buddy?
Something in your eye?</font></b>

792
01:17:53,502 --> 01:17:55,337
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yeah! You're the Viking!</font></b>

793
01:18:33,084 --> 01:18:34,209
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Dad?</font></b>

794
01:18:52,978 --> 01:18:54,396
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You got it, bud.</font></b>

795
01:18:57,233 --> 01:18:58,358
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hiccup!</font></b>

796
01:19:00,861 --> 01:19:04,072
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm sorry... for everything.</font></b>

797
01:19:04,490 --> 01:19:05,573
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yeah. Me, too.</font></b>

798
01:19:05,991 --> 01:19:07,617
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You don't have to go up there.</font></b>

799
01:19:08,327 --> 01:19:11,663
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">We're Vikings. It's an
occupational hazard.</font></b>

800
01:19:13,040 --> 01:19:16,000
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm proud to call you my son.</font></b>

801
01:19:17,420 --> 01:19:18,420
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Thanks, Dad.</font></b>

802
01:19:24,510 --> 01:19:25,802
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He's up!</font></b>

803
01:19:28,681 --> 01:19:30,223
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Get Snotlout out of there.</font></b>

804
01:19:30,391 --> 01:19:31,641
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- I'm on it!
- I'm on it first!</font></b>

805
01:19:31,809 --> 01:19:33,370
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Hey, let me drive!
- I'm ahead of you.</font></b>

806
01:19:33,519 --> 01:19:34,978
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No, this way.</font></b>

807
01:19:35,146 --> 01:19:37,355
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Don't push me!
- I'll take your teeth out!</font></b>

808
01:19:41,402 --> 01:19:43,153
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I can't believe that worked!</font></b>

809
01:19:50,369 --> 01:19:51,703
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Night Fury!</font></b>

810
01:19:51,871 --> 01:19:53,621
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Get down!</font></b>

811
01:20:03,507 --> 01:20:04,549
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Did you get her?</font></b>

812
01:20:15,060 --> 01:20:16,060
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Go.</font></b>

813
01:20:16,228 --> 01:20:20,607
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That thing has wings. OK,
let's see if it can use them!</font></b>

814
01:20:36,582 --> 01:20:38,583
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You think that did it?</font></b>

815
01:20:43,506 --> 01:20:45,256
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, he can fly.</font></b>

816
01:21:06,111 --> 01:21:08,821
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">OK, Toothless,
time to disappear.</font></b>

817
01:21:08,989 --> 01:21:10,240
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Come on, bud!</font></b>

818
01:21:16,288 --> 01:21:17,956
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Here it comes!</font></b>

819
01:22:10,301 --> 01:22:11,634
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Watch out!</font></b>

820
01:22:13,804 --> 01:22:16,139
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">OK, time's up! Let's
see if this works.</font></b>

821
01:22:18,934 --> 01:22:20,935
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Come on! Is that the
best you can do?!</font></b>

822
01:22:38,829 --> 01:22:41,205
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Stay with me, buddy.
Just a bit longer.</font></b>

823
01:22:45,878 --> 01:22:47,503
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hold, Toothless.</font></b>

824
01:22:48,297 --> 01:22:49,422
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Now!</font></b>

825
01:23:13,530 --> 01:23:14,530
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No.</font></b>

826
01:23:15,032 --> 01:23:16,407
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No!</font></b>

827
01:23:32,132 --> 01:23:32,632
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hiccup!</font></b>

828
01:23:37,554 --> 01:23:38,805
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Son!</font></b>

829
01:23:41,850 --> 01:23:42,934
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hiccup.</font></b>

830
01:24:04,707 --> 01:24:06,374
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, son.</font></b>

831
01:24:07,960 --> 01:24:09,419
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I did this.</font></b>

832
01:24:39,199 --> 01:24:42,493
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, son, I'm so sorry.</font></b>

833
01:24:49,168 --> 01:24:50,168
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hiccup!</font></b>

834
01:24:56,967 --> 01:24:59,969
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He's alive. You brought
him back alive.</font></b>

835
01:25:16,987 --> 01:25:19,906
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Thank you for saving my son.</font></b>

836
01:25:20,699 --> 01:25:23,701
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, you know... most of him.</font></b>

837
01:25:42,012 --> 01:25:43,596
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hey, Toothless.</font></b>

838
01:25:44,473 --> 01:25:46,724
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm happy to see you, too.</font></b>

839
01:25:49,895 --> 01:25:52,480
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm in my house.</font></b>

840
01:25:53,607 --> 01:25:55,483
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You're in my house.</font></b>

841
01:25:55,734 --> 01:25:57,401
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Does my Dad know you're here?</font></b>

842
01:25:57,569 --> 01:25:59,737
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What? OK, OK.</font></b>

843
01:26:00,239 --> 01:26:02,323
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Toothless, no. No, Toothless.</font></b>

844
01:26:02,491 --> 01:26:04,617
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Toothless! Oh, come on.</font></b>

845
01:26:43,365 --> 01:26:45,867
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">OK. Thanks, bud.</font></b>

846
01:26:56,545 --> 01:27:00,089
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Toothless, stay here.
- Come on, guys. Get ready!</font></b>

847
01:27:00,257 --> 01:27:01,507
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hold on tight! Here we go!</font></b>

848
01:27:04,761 --> 01:27:05,887
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What?</font></b>

849
01:27:14,146 --> 01:27:16,355
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I knew it. I'm dead.</font></b>

850
01:27:17,482 --> 01:27:21,485
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No, but you gave it your best shot.
So, what do you think?</font></b>

851
01:27:21,653 --> 01:27:23,321
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hey, look, it's Hiccup!</font></b>

852
01:27:24,740 --> 01:27:25,990
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's Hiccup!</font></b>

853
01:27:27,826 --> 01:27:31,662
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Turns out all we needed was
a little more of this.</font></b>

854
01:27:31,830 --> 01:27:33,915
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You just gestured to all of me.</font></b>

855
01:27:35,000 --> 01:27:38,127
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, most of you. That
bit's my handiwork.</font></b>

856
01:27:38,587 --> 01:27:41,797
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">With a little Hiccup flair thrown in.
You think it'll do?</font></b>

857
01:27:42,174 --> 01:27:44,258
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I might make a few tweaks.</font></b>

858
01:27:46,136 --> 01:27:47,970
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That's for scaring me.</font></b>

859
01:27:48,138 --> 01:27:50,681
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What is it always going to be this way?
'Cause...</font></b>

860
01:27:53,268 --> 01:27:54,810
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I could get used to it.</font></b>

861
01:27:58,023 --> 01:27:59,857
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Welcome home.</font></b>

862
01:28:00,025 --> 01:28:02,318
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Night Fury!
- Get down!</font></b>

863
01:28:13,455 --> 01:28:14,455
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You ready?</font></b>

864
01:28:16,583 --> 01:28:19,085
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">This is Berk.</font></b>

865
01:28:19,544 --> 01:28:23,339
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It snows 9 months of the
year and hails the other three.</font></b>

866
01:28:24,800 --> 01:28:28,636
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Any food that grows here
is tough and tasteless.</font></b>

867
01:28:30,180 --> 01:28:33,307
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The people that grow
here are even more so.</font></b>

868
01:28:37,187 --> 01:28:39,313
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The only upsides are the pets.</font></b>

869
01:28:42,234 --> 01:28:45,987
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">While other places have
ponies or parrots...</font></b>

870
01:28:47,322 --> 01:28:48,864
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">we have...</font></b>

871
01:28:49,908 --> 01:28:51,325
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">dragons.</font></b>